        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"307953\">Ruben Van de Velde</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/116395-maths/topic/Riemann.20zeta/near/345519488\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Planning to submit it to mathlib before we're done porting? :)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I'm currently drip-feeding bits of it into mathlib3, and making companion mathlib4 PR's for the parts which touch already-ported files. At some point I'll switch over to making mathlib4 PR's, but given that this proof depends on virtually the entire analysis library (measure theory, integration, Fourier analysis, Poisson summation...), that's not going to be any time soon.</p>",
